---
source: crates/loom/tests/cli_help.rs
expression: "loom_help(&[\"tune\"])"
---
Tune skills and templates through isolated proposals

Usage: loom tune [OPTIONS] [COMMAND]

Commands:
  skill    List or tune skills
  phase    List or tune phase templates
  partial  List or tune partial templates
  checker  List registered tuning checkers
  all      List or tune every tuneable surface
  help     Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -w, --workspace <PATH>  Workspace root. Defaults to the current working directory
      --host-key          Explicitly allow ambient host Git credentials and signing config
  -A, --agent <BACKEND>   Override the agent backend for this invocation [possible values: claude, pi, direct]
  -h, --help              Print help
